#: ../../M/macdink.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from the Apple Macintosh, which is said to encourage such behavior] To make"
" many incremental and unnecessary cosmetic changes to a program or file. "
"Often the subject of the macdinking would be better off without them. \"When"
" I left at 11PM last night, he was still macdinking the slides for his "
"presentation.\" See also :ref:`fritterware`\\, :ref:`window-shopping`\\."
msgstr ""
"[そのような振る舞いを助長すると言われるApple "
"Macintoshから]プログラムやファイルに、多くの段階的で不必要な見た目の変更を加えること。しばしばmacdinkingの対象はそれらなしのほうがよい。「昨晩11時に帰ったとき、彼はまだプレゼンのスライドをmacdinkingしていた」。\\"
" :ref:`fritterware`\\ 、\\ :ref:`window-shopping`\\ も参照。"
